---
layout: base.njk
showHomeLink: false
---

{% set postBackHref = page | postBackUrl(work, collections) | url %}
{% set postAbsoluteUrl = page.url | absoluteUrl(site) %}
{% set xPostHref = "https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=" ~ ("ネタバレ注意" | encodeURIComponent) ~ "&url=" ~ (postAbsoluteUrl | encodeURIComponent) %}

<h1>{{ work | workName }}</h1>

<article class="post post-single spoiler-gated" id="{{ page | postAnchor }}" data-spoiler-gate>
  <div class="spoiler-content">
    {{ content | safe }}
    <time datetime="{{ date.toISOString() }}">
      {{ date.toLocaleString("ja-JP", {
        timeZone: "Asia/Tokyo",
        year: "numeric",
        month: "numeric",
        day: "numeric",
        hour: "2-digit",
        minute: "2-digit",
        hourCycle: "h23"
      }) }}
    </time>
  </div>

  <div class="spoiler-cover">
    <p>この投稿には作品のネタバレが含まれます。</p>
    <button type="button" class="spoiler-open-button">ネタバレを表示</button>
  </div>
</article>

<p class="home-link post-actions post-back-link">
  <a href="{{ postBackHref }}">作品ページのこの投稿へ戻る</a>
  <a href="{{ xPostHref }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Xへ投稿</a>
</p>
